		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I really rather loathe the oldschool hunt-n-peck text-entry methods. Password and name entry is easily my least favorite part of older games ... so much so that I'll often choose names like &quot;Aaaa&quot;.<br /><br />Certainly part of the point of the hunt-n-peck screens is &quot;no learning needed&quot;, but I'm not certain how something like the flower, where everything's on screen, is any worse.

		

